{"tid":647956,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老雙手撐幕門阻開車 令列車不能開走","createTime":"2018-04-30T09:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T10:17:12.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2376ecfb27c007e7dfaff99cbbaa68c5e0b9912e","tid":647956,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/df0LYq3vU0KvgLQ6nABA8A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/b5a70d5e19c066247a40afc5bcbcfa85\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fdf0LYq3vU0KvgLQ6nABA8A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fb5a70d5e19c066247a40afc5bcbcfa85&h=e66e7f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部分上了年紀的香港人，總覺得自己有「超能力」，例如在車來車往的馬路上，兩臂一張，便以為能夠像摩西分開紅海般，把兩邊的車輛煞停。近日網上亦流傳「港鐵摩西」的相片，一名阿伯相信為了趕車，以雙手撐住港鐵月台幕門，令列車不能開走。由於他的動作太誇張，惹來網民瘋狂改圖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨日有網民在Facebook群組「巴打絲打Facebook Club」上載圖片，斥責一名自私阿伯用手撐着港鐵的月台幕門，試圖令車門重新打開，全車乘客無辜受阻。有目擊者指，最後車長屈服，阿伯成功上車。發文者不禁直斥：「自私X上唔到車可以點？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相片不足一天已獲近3000個讚好，網民怒斥阿伯「趕住去投胎」，而他雙手撐門的畫面，更成為最新「潛力圖」。網民紛紛把相片改成「港鐵摩西」、「港鐵Iron Man」、「港鐵艾斯」等趣怪圖片。有人更發現畫面與衞生署標誌不謀而合。亦有人打趣地建議港鐵安裝電鋸幕門，以杜絕「衝門」乘客。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n景景：成架車等佢一個，依家啲人愈老愈仆X。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCY Kelvin 成個衞生署logo真人版。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOctopu-Heidi Hung：你咪就係傳說中將個紅海分開咗嗰個阿伯？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJackson：廢老睇完marvel之後，扮Captain America頂住閘門。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJohn Washington KT Fung ： 所以話，港鐵應該安裝電鋸車門同電鋸幕/閘門。"},{"pid":"ceaec299d9aff1c9fc90bd4e91d4dce2881d9f97","tid":647956,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e7516e0b2045f9a69a4b850823061339216deb","tid":647956,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:32:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da545b815277e880c5edd91c1bbfe28b89febdcd","tid":647956,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90e7516e0b2045f9a69a4b850823061339216deb","tid":647956,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:32:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:09:10.000Z","msg":"廢老會日日擋門確保唔會變舊聞"},{"pid":"c599437b4810bd3cc12e85bdcbc16a7685e3afe1","tid":647956,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:17:12.000Z","msg":"magneto?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}